<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>About - TodoApp</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      background: #f2f5f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    .navbar {
      background: #4caf50;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 30px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #4caf50;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      .navbar {
        flex-direction: row;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .nav-links {
        gap: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <div class="navbar">
    <h1>TodoApp</h1>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About TodoApp</h2>
    <p><strong>TodoApp</strong> is a simple and efficient task management tool designed to help you stay organized and productive. Whether you're managing daily chores, planning a project, or keeping track of personal goals, TodoApp provides a clean and intuitive interface to manage your tasks.</p>

    <p>This app was built with modern web technologies like <strong>HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</strong>, and can be powered by backend frameworks like <strong>Express.js</strong> for full functionality like task persistence, updates, and deletions.</p>

    <p>The responsive layout ensures a smooth experience across devices, making it easy to stay productive on-the-go from your desktop, tablet, or smartphone.</p>

    <p>If you have any feedback or suggestions, feel free to get in touch!</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
